<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841124663053061.png" title="1715841124663053061.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142828.png" width="790" height="370" style="width: 790px; height: 370px;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.57em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为切实践行习近平总书记关于“推动全民阅读、建设书香社会”的重要论述指引，充分发挥入党积极分子在全民阅读活动中的模范带头作用，引导广大青年深入阅读、积极思考，培养爱国爱党、勇于担当的时代新人，推动主题教育成果落地见效，经济管理学院第31期入党积极分子学班于2024年5月8日晚18时，在A10-115教室开展以“奋辑争先·书香致远”为主题的读书分享会，由班长吴梓鑫主持会议，第31期全体入党积极分子参加。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">本次读书分享会主要分为四个部分：</span></p><section data-role="list" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-role="list" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1.第31期学班班长吴梓鑫做会议要求；</span></p><section data-role="list" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2.集体学习-小组讨论；</span></p><section data-role="list" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.小组代表分享心得；</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">4.发展对象负责人郭名滦做会议总结。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841245778010072.png" title="1715841245778010072.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142839.png" width="939" height="461" style="width: 939px; height: 461px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会议伊始，第31期班长吴梓鑫对本次读书分享会做出要求，他指出，之所以举办这场读书分享会，是为了更好的弘扬阅读之气，做时代先锋。读书对一个人是有很多帮助的：读书使人明智、读书使人心旷神怡、读书使人提高境界......一代名儒朱熹有云：“书犹药也，善读之可以医愚。”希望各入党积极分子，借本次分享会的契机，通过阅读红色经典，传承红色基因，赓续红色血脉，了解红色事迹，我们才能够更好的去了解共和国的光辉历史，增强民族凝聚力和自豪感。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841309678000556.png" title="1715841309678000556.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142846.png" width="933" height="463" style="width: 933px; height: 463px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（入党积极分子认真学习中）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841369293094713.png" title="1715841369293094713.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142854.png" width="935" height="563" style="width: 935px; height: 563px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">领学结束后，进入本次分享会的第二项议程，由各小组组长组织进行小组讨论，讨论现场气氛活跃。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: none; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841459956038805.png" title="1715841459956038805.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142900.png" width="935" height="604" style="width: 935px; height: 604px;"/></span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学员们畅所欲言，各抒己见，相互探讨，分享着自己近期学习的红色书籍内容及阅读感悟。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841570841014341.png" title="1715841570841014341.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142906.png" width="941" height="600" style="width: 941px; height: 600px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学员们在聆听他人的分享感悟时，也会随手记下自己感兴趣和认为有意义的部分。不少学员表示，通过本次读书分享会，自己对红色书籍意义的认识更深了，对红色书籍的阅读兴趣也更浓了。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841620376054788.png" title="1715841620376054788.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142911.png" width="946" height="510" style="width: 946px; height: 510px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841659146098409.png" title="1715841659146098409.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142920.png" width="945" height="493" style="width: 945px; height: 493px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（B230508班杜炫祺分享读书心得过程中）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">《红岩》展现了共产党人在艰难困苦中的坚定信念和英勇斗争精神，以及他们为了民族解放和人民幸福而作出的巨大牺牲。这部作品具有深远的历史意义和文学价值，被誉为“革命的教科书”。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“红岩精神”体现了中国共产党人的团结精神和奋斗精神，故作为入党积极分子的我们更应该始终保持对新时代中国特色社会主义事业的团结和奋斗精神，积极投身到各项工作中去，为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦贡献自己的力量。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841815380090295.png" title="1715841815380090295.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142926.png" width="955" height="493" style="width: 955px; height: 493px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（B230508<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">班<span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">黄通</span></span>分享读书心得过程中）</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">《钱学森传》全书由著名作家叶永烈编著，通过丰富的史料和生动的笔触，真实记录了钱学森的非凡人生和崇高风范。</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">书中不仅讲述了钱学森的学术成就和科研经历，还深入剖析了他的成长历程、性格特点以及对中国科技事业的巨大贡献。书中穿插了大量珍贵的照片和第一手资料，使读者能够更加直观地了解这位科学巨匠的传奇人生。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">结合二十届二中全会和党的二十大精神，我深刻地认识到，科技创新是国家发展的核心动力，是推动社会进步的关键。钱学森先生正是以他的聪明才智和无私奉献，为我国航天科技事业奠定了坚实的基础。他的事迹激励着我们，要勇攀科技高峰，不断创新突破，为国家的现代化建设贡献自己的力量。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">品读《钱学森传》让我更加坚定了自己的信念，我将以钱学森先生为榜样，努力学习，勇于创新，为实现国家的科技强国梦贡献自己的一份力量。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715841937490093879.png" title="1715841937490093879.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142933.png" width="972" height="485" style="width: 972px; height: 485px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（B230502</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;">班</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">周欣怡</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">分</span></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">享读书心得过程中）</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">《红星照耀中国》的作者</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">埃德加·斯诺</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">打破了新闻封锁，让西方人看到在贫瘠的中国西北土地上，那些共产党人正在为争取民主独立而进行极其艰苦的斗争，这些人的使命感、远见卓识和百折不挠的精神，是中华民族的希望之光。斯诺的报道相当程度上改变了当时国际上对</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“红区”的偏见，这是了不起的新闻之伟力。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我认为这本书强调了中国共产党与人民群众之间的紧密联系。在书中，我们可以看到中国共产党始终把人民群众的利益放在第一位，为他们谋福利、解难题。这种以人民为中心的思想，是我们今天在工作中应该牢记的原则。只有真正关心人民群众的疾苦和需求，才能得到他们的信任和支持。此外，我还从这本书中领悟到了团结协作的重要性。在书中，我们可以看到中国共产党内部团体之间的合作和协调，是如何让革命事业取得胜利的。这种团结协作的精神，也是我们今天在工作中应该注重的品质。只有紧密团结在一起，才能战胜各种困难和挑战。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715842029109013748.png" title="1715842029109013748.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142941.png" width="967" height="488" style="width: 967px; height: 488px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（B230503</span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;">班<span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">宋忆茹</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">分</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">享读书心得过程中）</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: red; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">《习近平与大学生朋友们》通过25篇访谈实录，讲述了习近平同志自工作以来，与大学生们交往交流交心的故事，真实表现了他对大学生始终如一的关注、关心、关爱。他教导大学生们要志存高远、脚踏实地、行循自然、自找苦吃，学习时要学会给书本上的知识“挤挤水”。</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">青年是祖国的未来，中华民族的接力棒传递到了青年手中。作为入党积极分子，我们应当牢记总书记的殷殷嘱托，直面人生曲折，笑对风雨坎坷，在为祖国、为人民、为民族、为人类的奉献中彰显青春力量、实现个人价值，让青春之光照亮伟大复兴梦想的前进！</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715842163549095649.png" title="1715842163549095649.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142947.png" width="969" height="490" style="width: 969px; height: 490px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">（B230505</span><span style="text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;">班<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; text-indent: 30.9999px;">万俊豪</span></span><span style="text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">分</span><span style="text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">享读书心得过程中）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在《习近平总书记的知青岁月》中，习近平总书记这样总结他的知青岁月：“15岁来到黄土地时我迷茫彷徨，22岁离开黄土地时，我已经有着坚定的人生目标，充满自信。”在阅读本书和查阅相关资料的过程中，我被习近平总书记那种坚韧不拔，勇往直前的精神所感动，他在农村插队时，尽管面临艰苦的生活条件和工作环境，但他始终保持着对党和人民的忠诚，对工作的热情。作为入党积极分子的我们应该学习习近平总书记能吃苦、敢担当、肯奋斗的精神。在读书这条路上，无论外界环境多么艰苦，仍然要不断读书，不断学习。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715842252243003731.png" title="1715842252243003731.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 142958.png" width="978" height="494" style="width: 978px; height: 494px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">（B230505</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%;">班</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);"><span style="text-align: center; text-indent: 30.9999px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">潘舒灵</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; caret-color: red; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">分</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">享读</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">书心得过程中）</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">《邓小平在江西日子里的思考》讲述了邓小平同志因文革而被下放到江西8年的人生经历。翻开这本书，我仿佛回到了那个波澜壮阔的年代，了解小平同志的“三落三起”和伟大成就。在这八年中，小平同志每天参加劳动、看书、看报、听广播，密切关注时事。参加劳动、与工人师傅们的朝夕相处、在江西一些地方的参观，使他了解了民众生产生活情况和当时社会的基本情况。小平同志大量阅读马列著作和中外史学、哲学著作，并结合基层实践将这些理论与中国实际结合起来。开创了改革开放的伟大先河。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-color: var(--msg-pop-bg-color-text-voice); text-align: left; caret-color: red; line-height: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">作为一名入党积极分子，我将铭记小平同志的伟大精神，永葆入党初心，积极向党组织看齐。在生活、工作中要严格要求自己，努力学习，不停思考，为实现中华民族伟大复兴贡献青春力量。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715842736030033456.png" title="1715842736030033456.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 143007.png" width="970" height="493" style="width: 970px; height: 493px;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">会议最后，由发展对象负责人郭名滦对本次的读书分享会进行总结，他首先赞赏了31期入党积极分子们在本次分享会中表现出的积极态度和营造出的活跃氛围，鼓励要将这种学班风貌一直延续下去。同时，他提醒各入党积极分子要时刻以党员标准严格要求自己，时时处处起模范带头作用，做到走在前，勇争先，善作为。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 16, 18); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240516/1715842537422073801.png" title="1715842537422073801.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-16 143029.png" width="990" height="493" style="width: 990px; height: 493px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（入党积极分子认真听讲中）</span><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">至此，经济管理学院第31期入党积极分子读书分享会圆满结束。本次集体学习中通过对红色书籍阅读分享、交流讨论的形式，既提升了入党积极分子对于红色书籍的阅读鉴赏能力，也推动了入党积极分子之间的思想碰撞与共同成长，还增进了入党积极分子对党的历史、理论和政策的了解，增强了其党性修养。</span></p>